♪Terikat takdir, kita bertarung tanpa jalan pulang♪

4
00:00:22,630 --> 00:00:24,790
♪Sekali bertindak, tiada penyesalan♪

5
00:00:24,790 --> 00:00:29,040
♪Mencabar bayangan ancaman♪

6
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:32,560
♪Membebaskan diri dari kekusutan♪

7
00:00:32,560 --> 00:00:38,280
♪Tersesat dalam gelap, peluru dingin menanti♪

8
00:00:38,960 --> 00:00:41,850
♪Hingga semuanya lenyap seperti asap♪

9
00:00:41,860 --> 00:00:44,980
=Permainan Sembunyi=

10
00:00:45,020 --> 00:00:47,940
=Episod 14=

11
00:00:48,870 --> 00:00:51,900
Letak pertaruhan, cepat, jangan lambat.

12
00:00:52,440 --> 00:00:54,360
Pemula Tanpa Nama

13
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:58,110
menentang Raja Pembunuh.

14
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,600
Kau berjaya jumpa aku.

15
00:01:04,160 --> 00:01:05,000
Boleh tahan juga.

16
00:01:07,320 --> 00:01:08,480
Sebenarnya, aku tak cari kau.

17
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:10,760
Zhang Ahua yang jumpa kau.

18
00:01:11,350 --> 00:01:12,560
Zhang Ahua?

19
00:01:15,930 --> 00:01:16,840
Siapa tu?

20
00:01:20,490 --> 00:01:22,120
Gadis muda yang kau bunuh.

21
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:24,200
Dia baru dua puluh satu tahun.

22
00:01:25,780 --> 00:01:26,840
Aku datang hari ini

23
00:01:27,600 --> 00:01:29,240
untuk menuntut bela bagi dia.

24
00:01:32,240 --> 00:01:33,280
Kau tak patut datang.

25
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:36,640
Di tempat lain, aku lepaskan kau,

26
00:01:37,080 --> 00:01:38,360
tapi bukan di sini.

27
00:01:40,110 --> 00:01:41,880
Ini tempat di bawah pengawasan Alamak.

28
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:47,120
Kau memang boleh mati di sini.

29
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:59,360
Rancangan kita bukan saja gagal.

30
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,000
Ia langsung di luar kawalan.

31
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:02,210
Saya yang salah sebab dia cedera.

32
00:03:05,460 --> 00:03:06,440
Jangan cakap macam tu.

33
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,520
Saya datang dengan harapan

34
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,840
kita boleh cari jalan penyelesaian.

35
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:18,120
Saya tiada rancangan.

36
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:21,120
Dia dah tak percayakan saya.

37
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:23,720
Kalau kita jumpa dia, apa seterusnya?

38
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,480
Saya pun tak tahu.

39
00:03:27,550 --> 00:03:29,320
Saya tak patut cadangkan rancangan ni.

40
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:30,880
Teruskan.

41
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:35,200
Saya tak faham.

42
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,120
Ramai yang sokong awak,

43
00:03:37,270 --> 00:03:38,440
lindungi awak.

44
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,280
Saya pun disuruh jauhi awak.

45
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,600
Tapi tengok awak sekarang,

46
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,400
Awak layak ke semua tu?

47
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,160
Saya terfikir

48
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,680
kalau kita jumpa dia,

49
00:04:07,130 --> 00:04:08,760
kita patut beritahu dia perkara sebenar.

50
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:09,600
Tak mungkin.

51
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:10,720
Langsung tak boleh.

52
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,120
Dia dah lalui banyak perkara.

53
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,400
Memori dia pun belum pulih.

54
00:04:14,100 --> 00:04:14,990
Sekarang mungkin

55
00:04:14,990 --> 00:04:16,560
keadaan mental dia sangat tak stabil.

56
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:18,640
Kalau dia kena lagi,

57
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:22,480
dia boleh hilang kawalan sepenuhnya.

58
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:23,840
Apa maksudnya?

59
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,840
Maksudnya dia akan hilang kewarasan.

60
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:28,760
Dan muncul personaliti pelindung.

61
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:31,360
Diri kedua ni tak berfikiran rasional.

62
00:04:31,610 --> 00:04:33,560
Sifat cemburu dan agresifnya sangat kuat.

63
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,640
Kalau tak dikawal segera,

64
00:04:36,540 --> 00:04:37,720
personaliti kedua ni

65
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:39,600
akan perlahan-lahan menguasai dirinya.

66
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:40,480
Mari, sekali lagi.

67
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:10,120
Saya akan jadikan semua yang bantu awak,

68
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:12,120
semua yang suka awak,

69
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,960
dan semua yang awak suka,

70
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:17,080
sebagai hadiah khas untuk awak.

71
00:05:37,230 --> 00:05:41,410
Anda Buddha, anda Rakshasa.

72
00:05:46,700 --> 00:05:48,680
Menang!

73
00:05:50,570 --> 00:05:52,250
Pemula Tanpa Nama menang.

74
00:05:58,460 --> 00:06:02,940
(Stesen Kereta Api)

75
00:06:10,490 --> 00:06:11,610
Masih ikut saya?

76
00:06:12,210 --> 00:06:13,130
Sampai awak naik.

77
00:06:13,770 --> 00:06:15,010
Sampai awak pergi dengan kereta api tu.

78
00:06:29,210 --> 00:06:30,610
- Apa?
- Songtai.

79
00:06:30,730 --> 00:06:31,570
Songtai!

80
00:06:31,850 --> 00:06:32,690
Songtai!

81
00:06:32,930 --> 00:06:33,770
Songtai!

82
00:06:33,970 --> 00:06:34,850
Awak buat apa?

83
00:06:36,170 --> 00:06:37,530
Semua, beri laluan.

84
00:06:40,090 --> 00:06:40,930
Berganjak!

85
00:06:53,050 --> 00:06:53,890
Ketua Wang,

86
00:06:54,930 --> 00:06:56,010
Saya akan berterus terang.

87
00:06:57,450 --> 00:06:59,450
Saya datang walaupun diburu.

88
00:07:03,450 --> 00:07:05,930
Orang macam kita, dipinggirkan,

89
00:07:06,250 --> 00:07:07,330
patut bergabung tenaga,

90
00:07:07,570 --> 00:07:08,650
dan cari kebenaran bersama.

91
00:07:11,010 --> 00:07:11,850
Macam mana?

92
00:07:14,050 --> 00:07:15,290
Hebat untuk orang muda.

93
00:07:16,130 --> 00:07:17,050
Tapi saya digantung tugas.

94
00:07:17,890 --> 00:07:18,730
Hal ni...

95
00:07:19,690 --> 00:07:20,530
Saya tak dapat bantu banyak.

96
00:07:24,250 --> 00:07:25,090
Saya siasat awak.

97
00:07:26,170 --> 00:07:27,010
Saya tahu.

98
00:07:27,530 --> 00:07:29,250
Awak bukan orang yang kaku.

99
00:07:33,330 --> 00:07:34,490
Oh, awak selidik saya?

100
00:07:36,050 --> 00:07:37,330
Saya pun cari maklumat tentang awak.

101
00:07:38,450 --> 00:07:40,210
Pegawai muda yang dipinjamkan.

102
00:07:41,050 --> 00:07:43,370
Resume awak agak rekaan.

103
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,490
Awak terlalu mencurigakan

104
00:07:44,490 --> 00:07:45,770
Saya tak sanggup pergi

105
00:07:45,770 --> 00:07:46,810
tanpa kebenaran.

106
00:07:48,570 --> 00:07:49,410
Lagipun,

107
00:07:50,370 --> 00:07:51,890
Saya ada tawaran yang awak tak boleh tolak.

108
00:08:13,690 --> 00:08:15,050
Setiap telefon simpanan saya

109
00:08:15,730 --> 00:08:17,570
ada nombor kontak tersendiri.

110
00:08:23,250 --> 00:08:24,090
Saya beri amaran,

111
00:08:25,250 --> 00:08:27,010
jangan cakap sembarangan dengan Han Xu.

112
00:08:27,890 --> 00:08:28,770
Dr. Chen dah cakap,

113
00:08:29,370 --> 00:08:30,810
kalau dia tertekan,

114
00:08:31,010 --> 00:08:32,010
dia akan hilang kewarasan.

115
00:08:32,250 --> 00:08:33,090
Tenang saja.

116
00:08:33,290 --> 00:08:35,010
Saya pun tak nak Ketua Han cedera.

117
00:08:35,730 --> 00:08:36,570
Jadi,

118
00:08:37,050 --> 00:08:37,890
Saya perlukan awak

119
00:08:38,850 --> 00:08:39,730
dan pasukan awak.

120
00:08:46,690 --> 00:08:47,530
Makan dulu.

121
00:08:50,410 --> 00:08:51,970
Saya tak nak makan.

122
00:08:52,570 --> 00:08:53,410
Mungkin beracun.

123
00:08:54,730 --> 00:08:55,570
Awak pula?

124
00:08:56,330 --> 00:08:57,170
Saya pun tak percaya.

125
00:09:44,370 --> 00:09:45,850
Saya sudah tunggu panggilan awak.

126
00:09:46,290 --> 00:09:47,130
Tuan.

127
00:09:48,850 --> 00:09:49,690
Ketua Han.

128
00:09:50,410 --> 00:09:51,410
Saya bukan musuh awak.

129
00:09:51,690 --> 00:09:52,850
Tapi bukan juga kawan saya.

130
00:09:54,170 --> 00:09:55,010
Mari kita jumpa.

131
00:09:56,290 --> 00:09:57,130
Saya boleh bantu awak.

132
00:09:59,210 --> 00:10:00,050
Baiklah.

133
00:10:00,410 --> 00:10:01,370
Tempat yang sama seperti dulu.

134
00:10:02,530 --> 00:10:03,370
Jam lapan malam ini.

135
00:10:04,810 --> 00:10:06,210
Saya harap kali ini apa yang saya nampak

136
00:10:07,210 --> 00:10:08,330
bukan mayat.

137
00:10:14,540 --> 00:10:17,420
(Wu; mungkin palsu)

138
00:10:20,410 --> 00:10:21,250
Saya akan tanya soalan.

139
00:10:21,450 --> 00:10:22,290
Jawab saja.

140
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:23,810
Jangan tambah apa-apa.

141
00:10:26,210 --> 00:10:27,290
Awak bukan Wu yang sebenar.

142
00:10:28,570 --> 00:10:29,410
Siapa awak?

143
00:10:30,570 --> 00:10:31,730
Saya dipinjamkan,

144
00:10:31,920 --> 00:10:33,050
seorang pegawai polis untuk kes ini.

145
00:10:35,250 --> 00:10:36,090
Nama saya Songtai.

146
00:10:38,730 --> 00:10:40,170
An Shaocong, Xiao Ran,

147
00:10:40,690 --> 00:10:41,690
dan Wu yang sebenar

148
00:10:42,410 --> 00:10:43,610
sudah mati dua bulan lepas, betul?

149
00:10:47,330 --> 00:10:48,730
- Ya.
- Kenapa awak berlakon?

150
00:10:48,930 --> 00:10:49,930
Rancangan balai.

151
00:10:50,850 --> 00:10:51,690
Penyiasatan semula kes.

152
00:10:52,730 --> 00:10:54,210
Tujuannya untuk mencetuskan awak

153
00:10:54,490 --> 00:10:55,610
supaya awak ingat semula.

154
00:10:57,290 --> 00:10:58,130
Tapi sekarang rancangan itu

155
00:10:58,610 --> 00:10:59,450
gagal.

156
00:11:00,250 --> 00:11:01,650
Jadi maksud awak,

157
00:11:03,110 --> 00:11:04,380
Xiao Ran dan An Shaocong

158
00:11:04,380 --> 00:11:05,240
bukan saya yang bunuh mereka?

159
00:11:07,930 --> 00:11:09,210
Jadi siapa yang sebenarnya buat?

160
00:11:10,650 --> 00:11:11,530
Saya beri amaran.

161
00:11:12,410 --> 00:11:14,050
Jangan cakap bukan-bukan pada Han Xu.

162
00:11:15,330 --> 00:11:16,180
Saya pun tak tahu.

163
00:11:16,180 --> 00:11:17,040
Biar saya tanya sekali lagi.

164
00:11:17,850 --> 00:11:19,090
Ada kaitan dengan Wang Mingcheng?

165
00:11:19,130 --> 00:11:20,120
Saya pun tak tahu.

166
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:21,110
Kalau bukan saya yang bunuh,

167
00:11:21,270 --> 00:11:22,290
kenapa mereka kejar saya?

168
00:11:24,450 --> 00:11:25,290
Ketua Ma

169
00:11:26,140 --> 00:11:27,820
meletakkan kematian Zhang Ahua

170
00:11:27,940 --> 00:11:28,980
dan pengawal itu ke atas awak.

171
00:11:29,340 --> 00:11:31,140
Rancangan itu ada masalah.

172
00:11:32,060 --> 00:11:32,900
Dalam balai,

173
00:11:32,900 --> 00:11:34,020
ada orang cuba jatuhkan awak.

174
00:11:37,500 --> 00:11:38,340
Bagaimana dengan Bilik 405?

175
00:11:39,060 --> 00:11:39,900
Saya tak jumpa apa-apa.

176
00:11:40,940 --> 00:11:42,140
Tapi semasa siasatan,

177
00:11:43,260 --> 00:11:44,420
saya jumpa sesuatu yang pelik.

178
00:11:45,740 --> 00:11:46,580
Apa dia?

179
00:11:48,380 --> 00:11:49,220
Xiao Ran.

180
00:11:51,540 --> 00:11:52,580
Dia bukan isteri awak yang sebenar.

181
00:11:56,350 --> 00:11:57,210
Xu.

182
00:11:57,220 --> 00:11:58,380
Bila kita nak keluar?

183
00:11:58,700 --> 00:11:59,620
Saya akan bawa Ran bersama.

184
00:11:59,900 --> 00:12:01,220
Saya tahu cara untuk keluar.

185
00:12:01,500 --> 00:12:03,100
Saya sudah bersedia untuk hadapi Xiao Ran.

186
00:12:03,100 --> 00:12:04,700
Isteri awak, Xiao Ran pun sudah tiada.

187
00:12:04,700 --> 00:12:06,340
Hanya yang mati tak berbahaya.

188
00:12:06,340 --> 00:12:07,180
Xu!

189
00:12:10,220 --> 00:12:11,060
Saya tahu

190
00:12:12,540 --> 00:12:13,660
susah untuk awak terima,

191
00:12:15,660 --> 00:12:16,500
tapi itulah kebenaran.

192
00:12:20,460 --> 00:12:21,580
Awak masih menipu!

193
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:45,360
♪Menunggu haruman bunga♪

194
00:12:46,480 --> 00:12:49,400
♪Untuk melintasi tembok tinggi♪

195
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:54,520
♪Menunggu tepi pantai♪

196
00:12:55,280 --> 00:12:59,080
♪Untuk lupakan badai♪

197
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:03,720
♪Begini saja♪

198
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:07,920
♪Membazir beberapa inci♪

199
00:13:07,920 --> 00:13:09,240
♪Cahaya siang♪

200
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:12,640
♪Separuh untuk kenangan♪

201
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:18,000
♪Separuh untuk impian♪

202
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:20,680
♪Oh, perahu kecil♪

203
00:13:20,880 --> 00:13:23,000
♪Ke mana kau pergi♪

204
00:13:23,400 --> 00:13:27,280
♪Tak perlu jawab♪

205
00:13:27,800 --> 00:13:30,000
♪Biarkan aku♪

206
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:32,240
♪Melihat kau hanyut pergi♪

207
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:36,440
♪Ke dalam cahaya senja♪

208
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:39,160
♪Jangan takut♪

209
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:41,480
♪Dunia ini♪

210
00:13:41,720 --> 00:13:45,760
♪Walau luas mana pun♪

211
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:48,640
♪Tetapi sentiasa ada♪

212
00:13:48,640 --> 00:13:50,640
♪Seseorang yang peduli♪

213
00:13:50,640 --> 00:13:54,600
♪Bersinar seperti rumah api♪

